# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s03_d4f48df1:

    # Amber "No way."
    Amber "Не может быть."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s03_a2e6358d:

    # Marina "Maybe... it’s further up the road?"
    Marina "Может... она чуть дальше по дороге?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s03_d4c0ddc5:

    # Amber "I can’t believe it. It’s gone."
    Amber "Поверить не могу. Она исчезла."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s03_a016bae3:

    # Marina "We could have just passed it."
    Marina "Мы могли просто проехать мимо нее."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s03_7e251151:

    # Amber "We weren’t even away that long! How can it be gone?"
    Amber "Мы ведь отлучились совсем ненадолго! Куда она могла испариться?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:116
translate spanish hwb_s03_a3015f77:

    # "We stare at the empty space that once housed a certain ugly green car."
    "Miramos el espacio vacío que antes albergaba un cierto coche verde feo."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:120
translate spanish hwb_s03_08ad37d7:

    # "I look in every conceivable direction, but there’s nothing, nothing but an ocean of sand and a never ending stretch of road."
    "Miro en todas direcciones imaginables, pero no hay nada, nada más que un océano de arena y una carretera interminable."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s03_1948f27e:

    # "Was it towed?"
    "¿Lo remolcaron?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:126
translate spanish hwb_s03_b84eaf18:

    # "No. Not out here, not this quick."
    "No. No aquí, no tan rápido."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:130
translate spanish hwb_s03_69aa6481:

    # Amber "Where the hell did it go?"
    Amber "Куда она, черт возьми, запропастилась?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:134
translate spanish hwb_s03_371a88b5:

    # Marina "Yeah, that is kind of weird, isn’t it?"
    Marina "Ага, это немного странно, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s03_80e8073e:

    # "Marina’s hand rests against her cheek as she looks on with only mild confusion, like she’s trying to solve a small mystery."
    "La mano de Marina descansa sobre su mejilla mientras observa con solo una leve confusión, como si intentara resolver un pequeño misterio."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s03_dc1f6c99:

    # Amber "Your car is missing! That’s more than a little ‘weird.’"
    Amber "Твоя машина исчезла! Это немного больше, чем просто “странно”."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s03_7d54ee2f:

    # Marina "Well, it’s actually my big brother’s car. He just lent it to me when he left for college."
    Marina "Ну, на самом деле это машина моего старшего брата. Он отдал ее мне, когда поступил в колледж."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:152
translate spanish hwb_s03_dd619e96:

    # Amber "Oh, well that makes everything better, then."
    Amber "Ах, вот оно что, тогда все не так страшно."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:156
translate spanish hwb_s03_cee675b3:

    # Marina "Really?"
    Marina "Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s03_7952a5d9:

    # Amber "{size=+10}No!{/size}" with hpunch
    Amber "{size=+10}Нет!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s03_4a73d61a:

    # "I let out a heavy sigh and press my fingers to my temple, attempting to massage away the stress and irritation."
    "Suelto un suspiro pesado y presiono mis dedos contra la sien, intentando masajear el estrés y la irritación."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s03_4697e3f3:

    # Amber "It was probably stolen. We’ll need to call the police."
    Amber "Похоже ее угнали. Нам нужно позвонить в полицию."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s03_53ee1e60:

    # Amber "You have a phone, right?"
    Amber "У тебя ведь есть телефон, так?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s03_6b725556:

    # Marina "I do, but…"
    Marina "Да, но…"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:186
translate spanish hwb_s03_ffec318b:

    # "Her voice trails off a cliff. What she said earlier echoes in my head."
    "Su voz se desvanece en un abismo. Lo que dijo antes resuena en mi cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:190
translate spanish hwb_s03_76e93db1:

    # Amber "That’s right, you said it was dead."
    Amber "Точно, ты же говорила, что он разряжен."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:194
translate spanish hwb_s03_c45092dc:

    # Amber "And I’m guessing you left it in your car?"
    Amber "И к тому же ты оставила его в машине? Так?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s03_18353721:

    # Marina "Yeah..."
    Marina "Угу..."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s03_5b0e917f:

    # Amber "Well that’s just great."
    Amber "Просто прекрасно."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s03_6a53d68a:

    # Marina "Don’t you have one?"
    Marina "А у тебя что, нет телефона?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s03_da29ac60:

    # Amber "Nope. Never needed one."
    Amber "Нет, он мне не нужен."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:214
translate spanish hwb_s03_8765b4ea:

    # Marina "Afraid no one would call you?"
    Marina "Боишься, что никто не будет тебе звонить?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:228
translate spanish hwb_s03_4148d7c5:

    # Amber "Not quite."
    Amber "Не совсем так."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:230
translate spanish hwb_s03_939e150b:

    # "I shield my eyes and look up at the dry sky. Its color has shifted to a glowing orange as sunset begins to settle over the distant valley peaks."
    "Me protejo los ojos y miro hacia el cielo seco. Su color ha cambiado a un naranja brillante mientras el atardecer comienza a posarse sobre los picos lejanos del valle."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s03_5a3bc1db:

    # "It’s going to get dark pretty soon."
    "Va a oscurecer bastante pronto."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s03_358bd5e8:

    # Marina "Don’t worry, Amber. I would call you!"
    Marina "Не расстраивайся, Эмбер. Я бы тебе звонила!"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s03_50407686:

    # "I can’t just leave her."
    "No puedo simplemente dejarla."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s03_a2c4aef8:

    # "Even if she did have her phone, it would take forever before anyone could get out here. She’d go from burning up in the heat to freezing out in the cold within a few hours."
    "Incluso si tuviera su teléfono, tardaría una eternidad en que alguien llegara hasta aquí. Pasaría de quemarse por el calor a congelarse por el frío en cuestión de horas."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s03_000aa0f6:

    # "Plus, if there are people around who would steal cars, then there’s no telling who else is out here."
    "Además, si hay gente por aquí que roba autos, quién sabe quién más anda por estos lugares."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s03_6fcd1ab5:

    # "I can already see how all this would go down. She would be huddled on the side of the road, trying to keep warm. A pack of coyotes would be howling all around her, closing in. Then, from down the road, a starved creep would pull up in a trashy old pickup truck, open his door for her, and…"
    "Ya me imagino cómo terminaría todo esto. Estaría acurrucada al borde del camino, tratando de entrar en calor. Una manada de coyotes aullaría a su alrededor, acercándose. Luego, desde la carretera, un tipo siniestro y hambriento llegaría en una camioneta vieja y destartalada, le abriría la puerta y..."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s03_dd17b7d8:

    # "Well, you already know how that part works out later in the story."
    "Bueno, ya sabes cómo sale esa parte más adelante en la historia."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s03_eacca17b:

    # "Oh god."
    "Ay, Dios."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s03_2147801c:

    # Amber "Hey, where’re you from, if you don’t mind me asking?"
    Amber "Эй, а где ты живешь, если не секрет?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s03_b5e5c638:

    # Marina "Oh, I’m from Carlsbad."
    Marina "О, я из Карлсбада."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s03_9dd26d3e:

    # "She pauses for a moment."
    "Se detiene un momento."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s03_aa234e59:

    # Marina "Or at least kinda close to it. It’s a little out of the way."
    Marina "Рядом с ним, если быть точнее. Это довольно далеко отсюда."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:288
translate spanish hwb_s03_dc64e378:

    # Amber "Carlsbad? You’re from California?"
    Amber "Карлсбад? Ты что, из Калифорнии?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:292
translate spanish hwb_s03_f607fd57:

    # Marina "No, silly. Carlsbad, New Mexico."
    Marina "Нет, глупенькая. Карлсбад, Нью-Мексико."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s03_bdc8b658:

    # Amber "Oh, uh, right."
    Amber "А, да, ясно."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s03_36f298f0:

    # "Had me going there for a second."
    "Casi me la crees por un segundo."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s03_c024c770:

    # Amber "How far’s that?"
    Amber "И насколько это далеко?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s03_05ff0bc7:

    # Marina "{cps=10}Hmm… {w=0.7}{/cps}{cps=4}Maaaaaay{/cps}{cps=80}be two hours from here?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=10}Хмм… {/cps}{cps=4}Гдееее{/cps}{cps=80}-тооо часа два езды отсюда?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s03_81feb7db:

    # Amber "Wow, you didn’t get very far at all, did you?"
    Amber "Воу, не так уж и далеко ты забралась, верно?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s03_3d524e4f:

    # "Marina lowers her head in shame."
    "Marina baja la cabeza avergonzada."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s03_0c8dad6a:

    # Marina "I never really seem to."
    Marina "Похоже на то."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s03_9803fc06:

    # "Though, I’m not really one to talk. I’ve been on the road less than a day. Would’ve gotten further if traffic on the I-40 wasn’t such a pain in the butt, or if I didn’t pick up Marina."
    "Aunque, no soy quien para hablar. Llevo menos de un día en la carretera. Habría llegado más lejos si el tráfico en la I-40 no fuera tan molesto, o si no hubiera recogido a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s03_0c87da48:

    # Amber "Hey, listen… You don’t live too far away. If you want, I can probably give you a lift back home."
    Amber "Эй, слушай, ты живешь не так и далеко. Если хочешь, могу подкинуть прямо до дома."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s03_b869f51f:

    # "I prep myself for an explosion of thankful energy and excitement."
    "Me preparo para una explosión de energía agradecida y emoción."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s03_779109f4:

    # "But there isn't one."
    "Pero no ocurre."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s03_87483f4f:

    # "Instead she continues to stare at the ground, her hands now balled up in a fist as she fidgets ever so slightly."
    "En cambio, sigue mirando al suelo, con las manos ahora apretadas en puños mientras se mueve ligeramente, inquieta."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s03_3437e4c3:

    # Amber "Something wrong?"
    Amber "Что-то не так?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s03_fe74246c:

    # "She shifts her gaze from the ground and looks me straight in the eyes, drawing a deep, long breath."
    "Desvía la mirada del suelo y me mira directamente a los ojos, respirando hondo y largo."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s03_915e2746:

    # Marina "Remember the treasure we were talking about at the store?"
    Marina "Помнишь, в том магазине мы говорили о сокровище?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s03_defadd0a:

    # Amber "Yeah."
    Amber "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s03_b180fcc1:

    # Marina "I know it’s a lot to ask, and you’ve already helped me out so much already."
    Marina "Я знаю, что прошу слишком многого, ведь ты уже и так достаточно для меня сегодня сделала..."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s03_c3eb8fd6:

    # Marina "But do you think you could take me the first place the treasure is?"
    Marina "Но не можешь ли ты отвезти меня к первому местоположению сокровища?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s03_1220824c:

    # Amber "Huh?"
    Amber "Чего-чего?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s03_e8dace69:

    # "She wants to keep going? Even after this entire disaster?"
    "¿Quiere seguir adelante? ¿Incluso después de todo este desastre?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s03_687be338:

    # Marina "The treasure! Could you take me to the first—"
    Marina "Сокровище! Не могла бы ты отвезти меня к—"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s03_b01149d7:

    # Amber "I heard ya the first time!"
    Amber "Я тебя и в первый раз услышала!"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:372
translate spanish hwb_s03_0d7099c2:

    # Amber "It’s just…"
    Amber "Просто…"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:376
translate spanish hwb_s03_27ab3d7a:

    # Amber "You don’t even know if this thing is real, but you’ve dropped everything to go look for it."
    Amber "Ты даже не знаешь, существует ли оно, но все равно бросила все и отправилась на поиски. "

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:380
translate spanish hwb_s03_153dcb07:

    # Amber "And now you’re asking me, someone you’ve {i}just{/i} met out in the middle of the desert, to take you to it."
    Amber "И теперь ты просишь меня, человека, которого {i}только что{/i} встретила посреди пустыни, отвезти тебя к нему."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:384
translate spanish hwb_s03_6c0cc3fa:

    # Amber "EVEN THOUGH, you don’t know if it’s real, and have just had your car stolen."
    Amber "К ТОМУ ЖЕ, я повторяю, ты не знаешь существует ли оно, а твою машину угнали."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:388
translate spanish hwb_s03_51d50a63:

    # Amber "Did I catch all that?"
    Amber "Я ничего не упустила?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:392
translate spanish hwb_s03_4de81261:

    # Marina "Uh-huh."
    Marina "Не-а..."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s03_b1289513:

    # "Shameless."
    "Descarada."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s03_0833ae89:

    # "I’m at a loss for words."
    "Me quedo sin palabras."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:402
translate spanish hwb_s03_9cf77642:

    # "How do I even respond to that?"
    "¿Cómo se responde a eso?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s03_8a77f8f9:

    # "I try to recollect my thoughts, but only one word comes to mind:"
    "Intento ordenar mis pensamientos, pero solo una palabra me viene a la mente:"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s03_9e910b84:

    # Amber "Why?"
    Amber "Почему?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s03_f4557bd9:

    # "Marina shrugs."
    "Marina se encoge de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s03_5e10ff7a:

    # "Nothing more than that. She just shrugs."
    "Nada más que eso. Solo se encoge de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s03_f0c74990:

    # "I take a look at her—a good look. Her wavy hair has been dried out by the hot desert air. Her face is red and drenched in sweat, probably close to melting off her makeup. Even her nice clothes are a little ruffled."
    "La miro bien—de verdad. Su cabello ondulado se ha resecado por el aire caliente del desierto. Su cara está roja y empapada de sudor, probablemente a punto de derretirle el maquillaje. Hasta su linda ropa está un poco arrugada."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s03_c8d55b50:

    # "But despite all that, this cute, peppy girl wants to keep pressing on."
    "Pero a pesar de todo eso, esta chica linda y animada quiere seguir adelante."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s03_9c560c18:

    # "Even when most people would have just called it quits after the car broke down."
    "Incluso cuando la mayoría ya se habría rendido después de que el auto se descompusiera."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s03_207950d3:

    # "Even out here all by herself."
    "Incluso aquí sola."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s03_8ec9e5a7:

    # "For all I know, she could be some weirdo out to mug me and this is all some elaborate scheme."
    "Por lo que sé, podría ser una rara que quiere asaltarme y todo esto es un plan elaborado."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s03_28752c66:

    # "But she wants my help. {i}My help.{/i} It’s been awhile since anyone has needed that. It’s like an honor. Do I deserve that?"
    "Pero quiere mi ayuda. {i}Mi ayuda.{/i} Ha pasado tiempo desde que alguien necesitó eso. Es como un honor. ¿Merezco eso?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s03_8c351382:

    # "Probably not."
    "Probablemente no."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s03_599003b9:

    # "But she’s still asking. Why should I say no? I don’t have to be in California for another few weeks, and isn’t that why I’m taking this trip? To see the sights, for him."
    "Pero ella sigue preguntando. ¿Por qué debería decir que no? No tengo que estar en California hasta dentro de unas semanas, y ¿no es por eso que estoy haciendo este viaje? Para ver los lugares, por él."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s03_e0d88078:

    # "She’s a little excitable, and even more naive, but maybe I need a little bit of that. It’s a lot better than just being out here all by myself with nothing but the ghosts of my memories to keep me company. Even if it’s just for a little while."
    "Es un poco emocionable, y aún más ingenua, pero quizás necesito un poco de eso. Es mucho mejor que estar aquí sola, sin nada más que los fantasmas de mis recuerdos para hacerme compañía. Aunque sea solo por un rato."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s03_514c88d6:

    # Amber "Eh, why the hell not? Hop in."
    Amber "Эх, черт побери, почему бы и нет? Поехали!"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:465
translate spanish hwb_s03_65ca8eea:

    # Marina "For real?"
    Marina "Правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:467
translate spanish hwb_s03_f01211c7:

    # Amber "Yeah, for real."
    Amber "Да, правда."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:469
translate spanish hwb_s03_263dc55a:

    # Amber "But only until the first location. After that—"
    Amber "Но только до первого места. После этого—"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:476
translate spanish hwb_s03_94939b42:

    # "The breath is forced out of me by the sharp impact of Marina tackling my stomach. A warm, but damp, sensation wraps itself tightly around me, as deadweight snuggles up against my chest."
    "El aire se me escapa por el fuerte impacto de Marina abalanzándose sobre mi estómago. Una sensación cálida, pero húmeda, se envuelve firmemente a mi alrededor, mientras un peso muerto se acurruca contra mi pecho."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:481
translate spanish hwb_s03_af493566:

    # Marina "{cps=80}Thankyouthankyouthankyouthankyouthankyou!{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=80}Спасибоспасибоспасибоспасибо!{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s03_a02d85eb:

    # Amber "{cps=50}W-{w=0.3}What are you doing?{/cps}"
    Amber "{cps=50}Ч-{/cps}{cps=5}ч{/cps}то ты творишь?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:491
translate spanish hwb_s03_4ba5ddfb:

    # Marina "I’m hugging you, silly."
    Marina "Обнимаю тебя, глупышка."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:493
translate spanish hwb_s03_6b2c3942:

    # "My cheeks grow warmer with each passing second. I try to wiggle my way out, but she stays latched on, her grip getting tighter and tighter."
    "Mis mejillas se calientan más con cada segundo que pasa. Intento zafarme, pero ella se aferra, apretando cada vez más fuerte."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:497
translate spanish hwb_s03_eeacf5b3:

    # Amber "{cps=50}Marina please,{w=0.4} y-{w=0.4}you’re all sweaty.{/cps}"
    Amber "{cps=50}Марина, пожалуйста,{w=0.4} ты-{w=0.4}ты вся мокрая.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:504
translate spanish hwb_s03_536f4fc5:

    # Marina "Ah, sorry! I’m just super happy!"
    Marina "Ой, прости! Я просто ужасно рада!"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:506
translate spanish hwb_s03_d7a52c85:

    # "She unlatches herself, letting me clear my throat and recollect myself."
    "Se suelta, dejándome aclarar la garganta y recuperar la compostura."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:510
translate spanish hwb_s03_59bd6898:

    # Amber "Anyway, let’s get inside. I’m burning up out here."
    Amber "Ладно, давай зайдем внутрь. Тут слишком жарко."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:546
translate spanish hwb_s03_3bbf7bee:

    # "We clamber back inside the motorhome, leaving the dry hellishness behind."
    "Subimos de nuevo a la casa rodante, dejando atrás el infierno seco."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:550
translate spanish hwb_s03_c5bc8e32:

    # "I turn the ignition and let the AC blast away the RV’s stuffiness."
    "Enciendo el motor y dejo que el aire acondicionado disipe el aire viciado de la RV."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:552
translate spanish hwb_s03_72060e66:

    # "Letting out breaths of sweet relief, Marina and I collapse back into our seats."
    "Exhalando suspiros de alivio, Marina y yo nos desplomamos en nuestros asientos."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:554
translate spanish hwb_s03_6f696602:

    # Amber "Alright, so where’s the first piece of the treasure?"
    Amber "Ладно, где находится первая часть сокровища?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:559
translate spanish hwb_s03_3f79b3f9:

    # Marina "Um{cps=3}. . . {/cps}Well—"
    Marina "Ну{cps=3}. . . {/cps}в общем—"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:563
translate spanish hwb_s03_71829276:

    # Amber "You have no idea, do you?"
    Amber "Ты понятия не имеешь, так ведь?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:565
translate spanish hwb_s03_7baa1618:

    # Marina "{cps=85}That’s not true! The news said a part of it was somewhere here in New Mexico{w=0.7}—probably.{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=85}А вот и нет! В новостях сказали, что она где-то здесь, в Нью-Мексико.{w=0.7}—скорее всего.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:567
translate spanish hwb_s03_31fb98d6:

    # "I’m not surprised at all. Should have seen this coming."
    "No me sorprende en absoluto. Debí haberlo visto venir."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:573
translate spanish hwb_s03_f73e0db0:

    # Amber "You have the journal?"
    Amber "Дневник у тебя?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:577
translate spanish hwb_s03_07cc638e:

    # Marina "Yeah."
    Marina "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:581
translate spanish hwb_s03_1ca3e462:

    # "She hands the cheap, paperback book to me. The cover feels like it could fall apart at the turn of a page. The whole thing is fitting of its rustic design."
    "Me entrega el libro barato de bolsillo. La portada parece que podría deshacerse al pasar una página. Todo encaja con su diseño rústico."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:583
translate spanish hwb_s03_04c8cb29:

    # "I slide my thumb across the edges and flip through the pages. Thick forewords and passages commenting on the journal’s historical significance skip past my eyes, most long enough to be their own book."
    "Deslizo el pulgar por los bordes y hojeo las páginas. Prólogos extensos y pasajes que comentan la importancia histórica del diario pasan ante mis ojos, la mayoría lo suficientemente largos como para ser su propio libro."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:585
translate spanish hwb_s03_ed954648:

    # "Finally, a photocopied picture of one of the original entries appears, preserving the faded cursive lettering, the entire thing printed on the next page over."
    "Finalmente, aparece una foto fotocopiada de una de las entradas originales, preservando la escritura cursiva descolorida, todo impreso en la página siguiente."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:587
translate spanish hwb_s03_06852638:

    # "Crusting brown stains and wrinkles engrave the photo. Some of the writing has been scratched out too, like someone made mistakes and couldn’t erase them."
    "Manchas marrones y arrugas crustáceas graban la foto. Parte de la escritura también está tachada, como si alguien hubiera cometido errores y no pudiera borrarlos."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:591
translate spanish hwb_s03_4593f221:

    # "I hate to admit it, but for something that’s probably a sham, the thing looks pretty authentic."
    "Odio admitirlo, pero para algo que probablemente es una farsa, se ve bastante auténtico."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:599
translate spanish hwb_s03_e58eaf04:

    # "Yeah, I’m not reading all this crap. Where should I {i}actually{/i} start?"
    "Sí, no voy a leer toda esta basura. ¿Dónde debería empezar {i}de verdad{/i}?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:601
translate spanish hwb_s03_acc76711:

    # "Let’s see. If he left California, lived in Missouri, and supposedly hid something in New Mexico like Marina said, then what we’re looking for is likely a later entry."
    "Veamos. Si él salió de California, vivió en Misuri, y supuestamente escondió algo en Nuevo México como dijo Marina, entonces lo que buscamos probablemente sea una entrada posterior."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:605
translate spanish hwb_s03_bd20b615:

    # Amber "Ah, here we are."
    Amber "Ага, вот оно."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:622
translate spanish hwb_s03_68cc16c6:

    # Marina "What does it say?"
    Marina "Ну что там?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:626
translate spanish hwb_s03_6be2949d:

    # Amber "The gist of it is that it’s near a big rock and a bunch of little rocks."
    Amber "Тут сказано, что оно находится рядом с одним большим камнем и парочкой камней поменьше."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:630
translate spanish hwb_s03_0ae756e1:

    # Marina "That should narrow it down, right?"
    Marina "Это сужает круг, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:634
translate spanish hwb_s03_c1a5e328:

    # Amber "Yeah—to the entire state of New Mexico."
    Amber "Ага, что-то на уровне всего штата Нью-Мексико."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:638
translate spanish hwb_s03_8ecf1425:

    # "Marina gasps and lunges towards the journal, the muscles in her neck tensed and eyes wide with panic."
    "Marina jadea y se lanza hacia el diario, los músculos de su cuello tensos y los ojos muy abiertos por el pánico."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:640
translate spanish hwb_s03_fd5610d1:

    # Marina "That can’t be the only thing he mentioned! There has to be more!"
    Marina "Это не может быть единственной подсказкой! Должно быть что-то еще!"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:642
translate spanish hwb_s03_b8ec68c8:

    # "I raise the journal high above me so she can’t reach it, using my hand as a blockade against her head as she desperately tries to grasp for it."
    "Levanto el diario por encima de mí para que no pueda alcanzarlo, usando mi mano como un bloqueo contra su cabeza mientras ella intenta desesperadamente agarrarlo."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:646
translate spanish hwb_s03_f7b86503:

    # Amber "Sheesh, relax for a second. I actually have a pretty good idea of where it might be."
    Amber "Шшш, успокойся ты на секунду. У меня есть предположение насчет этого места."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:648
translate spanish hwb_s03_140aff06:

    # "She settles down, still stiff with anxiety, nibbling on the tip of her thumb."
    "Se calma, todavía rígida por la ansiedad, mordisqueando la punta de su pulgar."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:652
translate spanish hwb_s03_45763f9b:

    # "I lower the book back down and read over the entry one more time, just to make sure."
    "Bajo el libro de nuevo y releo la entrada una vez más, solo para asegurarme."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:654
translate spanish hwb_s03_846017e4:

    # Amber "There’s a part where he calls it a ‘winged rock.’"
    Amber "Тут есть момент, где он говорит о “крылатым камне”."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:656
translate spanish hwb_s03_4dd658ea:

    # Amber "Assuming my years of reading travel guides and brochures weren’t totally useless, then I’m pretty sure that’s a loose translation of what the Navajo used to call Shiprock."
    Amber "Если годы, потраченные мной на чтение книг и брошюр про путешествия, не прошли напрасно, то похоже, что речь идет о Шипроке – родине древнего племени Навахо."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:658
translate spanish hwb_s03_82c8a0dc:

    # Marina "There’s a ship out in the desert? Whoa…"
    Marina "Шип-рок? Тут есть корабль прямо в пустыне? Вааау."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:660
translate spanish hwb_s03_6dae7c0e:

    # "I peer over the journal. Marina’s imagination is going bonkers, her eyes alight as she tries to wrap her head around such a novelty even existing."
    "Miro por encima del diario. La imaginación de Marina se está volviendo loca, sus ojos brillan mientras intenta procesar que algo así exista."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:662
translate spanish hwb_s03_99e8a0d2:

    # Amber "How long have you lived in New Mexico?"
    Amber "Как долго ты живешь в Нью-Мексико?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:664
translate spanish hwb_s03_ae63af7b:

    # "Marina swells up with pride, only to deflate like a balloon before speaking, instead choosing to blow a misplaced strand of hair out of the way."
    "Marina se infla de orgullo, solo para desinflarse como un globo antes de hablar, optando en cambio por apartar un mechón de cabello fuera de lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:666
translate spanish hwb_s03_34a9ae9a:

    # Marina "All my life."
    Marina "Всю свою жизнь."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:670
translate spanish hwb_s03_332ba023:

    # "I sigh and slam the journal shut."
    "Suspiro y cierro el diario de golpe."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:674
translate spanish hwb_s03_c8ba6e8d:

    # Amber "It’s a small mountain near the border of New Mexico and Utah that’s vaguely shaped like a ship."
    Amber "Это небольшая гора недалеко от границы разделяющей Нью-Мексико и Юту, которая по своей форме немного напоминает корабль."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:678
translate spanish hwb_s03_7f5d7129:

    # Marina "Ohhhhhh, okay. That makes way more sense."
    Marina "Оууу, понятно. Звучит логично."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:680
translate spanish hwb_s03_229ff50f:

    # Amber "I’m surprised you haven’t heard of it. Thing’s a landmark."
    Amber "Я удивлена, что ты не слышала о ней. Это что-то вроде местной достопримечательности."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:682
translate spanish hwb_s03_8b587bb4:

    # Marina "Yeah…"
    Marina "Ага…"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:684
translate spanish hwb_s03_13281ec9:

    # Marina "But hey! At least I know now!"
    Marina "Да ладно тебе, зато теперь я знаю!"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:686
translate spanish hwb_s03_16cf107d:

    # "Shrugging, I put away the journal away and smirk. Misplaced as it might be, her cheeriness is a good mix-up from the norm."
    "Encogiéndome de hombros, guardo el diario y sonrío con suficiencia. Aunque esté fuera de lugar, su alegría es un buen cambio de lo normal."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:688
translate spanish hwb_s03_2347de10:

    # Marina "Do you think the treasure might be there?"
    Marina "Думаешь, сокровище находится там?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:692
translate spanish hwb_s03_cfb5fe72:

    # Amber "Dunno, but it’s worth a shot. We don’t have anything else to go on."
    Amber "Кто знает, но стоит проверить. Тем более, больше вариантов у нас нет."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:696
translate spanish hwb_s03_07f756ae:

    # Amber "Sure you don’t want me to just take you home?"
    Amber "Уверена, что не хочешь просто поехать домой?"

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:700
translate spanish hwb_s03_0133d907:

    # "Marina hesitates for a moment, turning to the windshield as if to dodge the question with her eyes."
    "Marina duda por un momento, girándose hacia el parabrisas como si quisiera esquivar la pregunta con la mirada."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:702
translate spanish hwb_s03_9a1de5e3:

    # Marina "No… I think I want to do this."
    Marina "Нет... я думаю, что хочу это сделать."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:706
translate spanish hwb_s03_438cfba4:

    # Amber "Alright then."
    Amber "Ясно."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:713
translate spanish hwb_s03_d6f3e100:

    # "I put the car in drive and look ahead."
    "Pongo el coche en marcha y miro al frente."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:715
translate spanish hwb_s03_ecce28a5:

    # "The sun has set, the blue shade of dusk rising up to take its place. I press down on the gas. Marina turns to me and smiles."
    "El sol se ha puesto, el tono azul del crepúsculo se alza para ocupar su lugar. Piso el acelerador. Marina se vuelve hacia mí y sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:717
translate spanish hwb_s03_6816dd16:

    # Amber "Let’s hit the road."
    Amber "Пора в путь."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:19
    old "You can read any previously seen entries at any time by clicking the journal button in the bottom right, or by pressing the ‘J’ key."
    new "Вы можете получить доступ к записям с помощью кнопки “Дневник” в правом нижнем углу, либо нажав клавишу “J”."

    # game/script/hwb_s03.rpy:40
    old "You can read any previously seen entries at any time by tapping the journal button in the bottom right."
    new "Вы можете получить доступ к записям с помощью кнопки “Дневник” в правом нижнем углу."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s03.rpy:783
    old "Driving until the sun sets"
    new "Driving until the sun sets"

